#: .\EMM_dreams.json
msgid "You have a strange dream about crabs."
msgstr "你做了一個關於螃蟹的怪夢。"

#: .\EMM_dreams.json
msgid "Your dreams give you a strange shelled feeling."
msgstr "你的夢境讓你產生一種奇怪的甲殼感。"

#: .\EMM_dreams.json
msgid "You dream of walking on a sandy beach."
msgstr "你夢見走在沙灘上。"

#: .\EMM_dreams.json
msgid ""
"For some reason you dream of your gloves.  They don't fit, and nothing seems"
" to help..."
msgstr "不知為何，你夢見了自己的手套。它們不合手，而且似乎什麼都無濟於事……"

#: .\EMM_dreams.json
msgid "You have a disturbing dream of walking sideways all the time."
msgstr "你做了一個令人不安的夢，夢見自己一直橫著走。"

#: .\EMM_dreams.json
msgid "Your vivid dream of living as a crab frightens you."
msgstr "你做了一個生動的夢，夢見自己像螃蟹一樣生活，這讓你感到恐懼。"

#: .\EMM_dreams.json
msgid "You dream of pinching zombies with your claws."
msgstr "你夢見用鉗子夾殭屍。"

#: .\EMM_dreams.json
msgid "You have a vivid dream of shedding your carapace. It feels good."
msgstr "你做了一個生動的夢，夢見自己蛻去甲殼。感覺很舒服。"

#: .\EMM_dreams.json
msgid "You have a strange dream about snakes."
msgstr "你做了一個關於蛇的怪夢。"

#: .\EMM_dreams.json
msgid "Your dreams give you a strange slithery feeling."
msgstr "你的夢境讓你產生一種奇怪的滑膩感。"

#: .\EMM_dreams.json
msgid "You have a weird dream of slithering on the ground."
msgstr "你做了一個怪夢，夢見自己在地上滑行。"

#: .\EMM_dreams.json
msgid "In your dream, you see a strangely serpentine image of yourself."
msgstr "在你的夢中，你看到了一個奇怪的、蛇形的自己。"

#: .\EMM_dreams.json
msgid "You have a terrifying dream of losing your legs."
msgstr "你做了一個可怕的夢，夢見自己失去了雙腿。"

#: .\EMM_dreams.json
msgid "You dream of silently moving in shadows."
msgstr "你夢見自己在陰影中無聲移動。"

#: .\EMM_dreams.json
msgid "You have a pleasant dream of coiling around your prey."
msgstr "你做了一個愉快的夢，夢見自己纏繞著獵物。"

#: .\EMM_dreams.json
msgid "You have a scary dream of running out of venom."
msgstr "你做了一個可怕的夢，夢見自己的毒液用完了。"

#: .\EMM_dreams.json
msgid "You have a strange dream about rabbits."
msgstr "你做了一個關於兔子的怪夢。"

#: .\EMM_dreams.json
msgid "Your dreams give you a strange twitchy feeling."
msgstr "你的夢境讓你產生一種奇怪的抽搐感。"

#: .\EMM_dreams.json
msgid "You dream of walking on a grassy meadow."
msgstr "你夢見走在長滿青草的牧場上。"

#: .\EMM_dreams.json
msgid "In your dream, you look in the mirror and see a rabbit."
msgstr "在你的夢中，你照鏡子，看到了一隻兔子。"

#: .\EMM_dreams.json
msgid "You have a weird dream of carelessly jumping around."
msgstr "你做了一個怪夢，夢見自己漫不經心地跳來跳去。"

#: .\EMM_dreams.json
msgid "You have a terrifying dream of being chased by a fox."
msgstr "你做了一個可怕的夢，夢見自己被狐狸追趕。"

#: .\EMM_dreams.json
msgid "You have a blissful dream of eating carrots all day."
msgstr "你做了一個幸福的夢，夢見自己整天都在吃胡蘿蔔。"

#: .\EMM_dreams.json
msgid "You have a pleasant dream of having your ears fondled and massaged."
msgstr "你做了一個愉快的夢，夢見自己的耳朵被撫摸和按摩。"

